	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> """Evacuation orders and warnings remained in effect, though several evacuation zones have been downgraded or lifted.

All schools in the Simi Valley Unified School District will be closed for the rest of the week, with students expected to return on Tuesday, the superintendent announced Wednesday afternoon. Schools were already scheduled to be closed Monday due to the Memorial Day holiday.

Authorities have not officially determined a cause of the fire, but police said someone using a tractor for brush clearance called to report the machinery struck a rock, possibly producing sparks that started the fire."""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> ;
